result.name: Starbucks

reviews.text:
much more comfortable than other starbucks! sofa seats and wifi and sockets. just not as conveniently located coz you need to walk a bit to the building if you ain’t working here.
friendly staff too.
There are quite a few Starbucks nearby. This one is comfortable comparing to the small ones those without proper seats
Nice place to sit down, could use more electric outlets.
Excellent place for long stay.

This used to be my favourite Starbucks - the drinks were made well, they were fast, and the staff went out of their way to be nice.

However, it seems like all the staff changed now! Not the first time they missed my order.

Today, I waited for 15 minutes before following up on my food order, after noticing all the people that ordered much after me receive their orders. The lady very impatiently said "it's coming!". They then proceed to give me the wrong order. Only when I said that is not mine and told them what I ordered again, did they heat up my correct food order.

Obviously they "missed" my order. I wouldn't mind if she just admit she missed it, rather than dismiss me impatiently. Very rude, and not what I expected at Starbucks.
